{"tid":667541,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"原來鷹眼拍嗰套the hurt locker咁撚正","createTime":"2018-05-17T00:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T06:03:56.000Z","uid":66943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ded8364b861dd4bc07b427c07c382a0bd1c95bdd","tid":667541,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:05:21.000Z","msg":"The Hurt Locker是一部於2008年上映的美國戰爭電影，為Kathryn Ann Bigelow執導，編劇Mark Boal於2004年以戰地記者身份在伊拉克戰場上的見聞所創作。以及由Jeremy Lee Renner (Hawkeye)、Anthony Mackie (Falcon)及Brian Timothy Geraghty提等擔任演出。電影的劇情背景為美伊戰爭，描述美國陸軍拆彈部隊的成員。<br />\n<br />\nJeremy Lee Renner 在2010年因主演Kathryn Ann Bigelow電影《The Hurt Locker》，獲得了第82屆奧斯卡金像獎最佳男主角的提名，他因此一炮而紅。<br />\n<br />\nAnthony Mackie 2009年因出演《The Hurt Locker》，他被提名2009年獨立精神獎最佳男配角。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://is3-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music/e4/18/c3/mzi.yysqbnfg.jpg/600x600bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis3-ssl.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FMusic%2Fe4%2F18%2Fc3%2Fmzi.yysqbnfg.jpg%2F600x600bf.jpg&h=10d3d537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鷹眼上身一槍一件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/080411_d19b3614a5210a6b0924a212d47e45e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F080411_d19b3614a5210a6b0924a212d47e45e2.jpg&h=7861837f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/080411_42766098a72b2b10f4eca2f27d9c6167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F080411_42766098a72b2b10f4eca2f27d9c6167.jpg&h=29808651&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d88ae9b22346057480d8f3b211babcde4c908cba","tid":667541,"uid":27324,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:08:01.000Z","msg":"唔係best movie既質素"},{"pid":"8c1f20b07d4c1a3e57b8a994f63f609c2c6fc65f","tid":667541,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy